imdb.plot outline: It revolves around Zhong Kui after he is cast into the mortal world without a memory of the past. In his desperate search to recover his identity, he gets acquainted with an unlikely set of friends and sets out on an adventure to fight evil for the sake of good.
imdb.title: Zhong Kui
